data.description: Magnificent Custom Built Mid Century Home w/ its park like setting is awaiting its new caretaker. With almost an acre of gorgeous landscaping you may findyourself looking forward to strolling out the walkout basement, the morning sunrises and private views from the back patio or XL sun room. Along with theserene backdrop you will find a ''Bullfrog'' 6-8 person hot tub which sits beneath a wonderful gazebo. When you walk through the front door the bright andcheery entryway welcomes you to this picture perfect MCM. This home boasts 5 bedrooms and 4 baths along with 2 fireplaces, hardwood floors and spectacularMCM finishes. Invisible fence, newer H2O tank. If you are looking for a home that is anything but cookie cutter - this one should not be missed. A2A
